metadata.name: Perfects love #1
metadata.description: Snap out of it! Flying away from the crypto market! To endless dreams! In worn patent leather walking shoes! Said the Enterprising Soccer ball Kelvin! Showing off his VR glasses shackles, made by an Shoemaker Norway! More than that, he loves his virtual glasses made by a realtor from Austria! With an open decent mouth! And he has a baseball helmet on his head, made by a Georgia notary! Every day I start out, then I cry my heart out!
